<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_XmlRpc_Value* currently uses string concatenation to build XML. This can lead to encoding issues, particularly when using utf-8 charsets.</p>

<p>If Zend_XmlRpc_Value_String can use htmlentities to encode strings to ISO-8859-1, PHP's DOM layer can build well-formed XML that can be UTF-8 safe.</p>

